org.apache.commons.dbcp.SQLNestedException: Cannot create PoolableConnectionFactory (Communications link failure)
修改mysql远程连接权限问题
	1.切换到mysql安装bin目录下
	2.mysql -u root -p 输入密码
	3.use mysql;
	4.show tables;
	5.select host from user;
	6.update user set host ='%' where user ='root';
	7.以管理员身份重启mysql    net stop mysql   net start mysql